    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1932-06-30T10:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1932-06-30T10:00:00-05:00" n="508"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d508">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">825.00 Revolutions/137: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in Chile</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_CWS1"
                        type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Culbertson</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Santiago</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1932-06-30T10:00:00-05:00"
                            >June 30, 1932—10 a.m.</date>
                        <lb/> [Received 11:25 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>112. My telegram No. 109, June 26, 5 p.m., and Department’s telegram No. 45, June
                    29, 5 p.m.<note n="19" xml:id="d508fn19">Neither printed.</note> Press report
                    dated June 27th was premature but <persName corresp="#p_CDA1">Cabero</persName>
                    resigned last night as member of the Junta because of refusal of Junta to adopt
                    his policy of a return to constitutional forms. <persName corresp="#p_PVE1"
                        >Eliseo Peña Villalón</persName>, a leader in the Radical Socialist Party,
                    takes his place. No other changes.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_CWS1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Culbertson</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
